Stan Lees Superhumans: Season 3
On Stan Lee's Superhumans 3 from H2, Stan Lee and the World's Most Flexible Man, Daniel Browning-Smith, travel the world testing the claims of real people who declare they have genuine superpowers.




3)  Human Fireball 
This time Stan wants Daniel to investigate four people who claim to have superhuman heat tolerance, performing potentially deadly demonstrations that push themselves, and the human body, to new limits
